title: Mike Dowd TWO NIGHT Special Event: Night Two
description:
Mike Dowd, former NYPD Officer and the subject of "The Seven Five" documentary came to LA from New York for a TWO NIGHT Special Event with Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt. This is the second night.

The first night can be found here: https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/mike-dowd-two-night-special/id558364221?i=363470850&mt=2
